query:
SELECT 
  sr.supplierId,
  s.companyName,
  sr.serviceType,
  sr.serviceLevel,
  sr.countryCode,
  sr.cityId,
  sr.rateUsdCents,
  sr.isServiceable,
  CASE 
    WHEN sr.cityId IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT('City: ', pc.cityName)
    ELSE 'Country-wide'
  END as rate_scope
FROM supplierRates sr
INNER JOIN suppliers s ON s.id = sr.supplierId
LEFT JOIN supplierPriorityCities pc ON pc.id = sr.cityId
WHERE sr.countryCode = 'AU'
  AND sr.isServiceable = 1
ORDER BY sr.supplierId, sr.serviceType, sr.serviceLevel
LIMIT 20;
